# 📊 Retail Analytics Insights

## 🔍 Key Findings

### 🧠 Customer Behavior

* Customers with higher tech-savvy scores prefer online shopping
* Hybrid customers use both online and offline platforms effectively

### 💰 Spending Patterns

* High-income customers spend more compared to low-income groups
* Impulse buying significantly increases customer spending

### 🛒 Shopping Preferences

* Customers who prefer physical interaction (touch & feel) spend more in stores
* Online shoppers place more frequent orders

### 🚚 Delivery & Returns

* Longer delivery times lead to higher return frequency
* Faster delivery improves customer satisfaction

### 🌱 Environmental Awareness

* Environmentally aware customers may prefer sustainable products

